&gt;He looks familiar...
&gt;He sounded familiar too, actually...
&gt;You focus on him instead of the bills.
&gt;&quot;...Larry?&quot;
&gt;He flinches.
&gt;&quot;Who&#039;s that?&quot;
&gt;He&#039;s trying to make his voice sound deeper.
