&gt;&quot;Hey, are you okay?&quot;
&gt;Obviously not, but it&#039;s all you can think to say.
&gt;She sniffles.
&gt;Her eyes are wet with tears.
&gt;She stares at the ground.
&gt;&quot;That man. Is he really your dad?&quot;
&gt;She shakes her head.
&gt;It looks like she&#039;s hesitant to speak.
